    "description": "<strong>一个无情的多人生存挑战。当背叛潜伏在每一个阴影中时，信任是脆弱的。</strong> 深入一个联盟不稳定如同你面对的恶劣条件一样的世界。你能否智胜朋友并存活下来？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/6ac01a54136373ff886688b85584c843.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=73 /></span><br><br>在<strong>12人多人模式</strong>中体验刺激和背叛，线上或通过局域网。合作完成任务并挺过冬天，但更重要的是，你能看穿你盟友中的欺骗吗？<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>多样的策略，独特的机制：</strong> 每一场游戏都有不同的展开。你会成为一个狡猾的破坏者还是一个专注的收集者？<br></li><li><strong>合作克服障碍并收集资源。</strong> 当地人不喜欢偷胡萝卜的访客，但你需要零食来度过冬天。<br></li><li><strong>隐身和策略：</strong> 利用地形对抗危险的环境。在隐藏处和密集的灌木丛之间导航，同时关注你的同伴——他们真的在帮忙吗？</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/60401ceb443a9d910ffdab2c2c8e036a.poster.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/60401ceb443a9d910ffdab2c2c8e036a.webm?t=1710217323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/0dd39919649fc4a31e3832c0dd9392d4.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=73 /></span><br><br><strong>如果你想过冬，你需要合作。</strong> 动态的时间和天气系统使得探索变得危险且不可预测。注意不要单独被困在寒冷中！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>准备并生存对抗<strong>危险的天气变化！</strong><br></li><li>注意时间并<strong>不要在夜晚迷路！</strong><br></li><li>寒冷会让你行动迟缓并变得脆弱，所以<strong>保持温暖！</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/2aeef22a9f69bc5e26ccf30d65573edf.poster.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/2aeef22a9f69bc5e26ccf30d65573edf.webm?t=1710217323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/0b2e4e742148ad3da04ca148e7132038.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=73 /></span><br><br><strong>在你的藏身处准备迎接不可预测的事物。</strong> 解锁新地图和升级，同时等待你的朋友们准备好玩。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>在你的家中藏身处放松并准备好</strong>，等待其他朋友加入。<br></li><li><strong>获得升级！</strong> 使用你收集的资源来解锁工具和升级，这将使你的任务更加容易。<br></li><li><strong>解锁新地图和区域</strong>供你和你的朋友探索。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/a536faa2907a7d0785e63a2935f63def.poster.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/a536faa2907a7d0785e63a2935f63def.webm?t=1710217323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/2e71901a617ae4671c4d54cea938435a.poster.avif?t=1710217323\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180890/extras/2e71901a617ae4671c4d54cea938435a.webm?t=1710217323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
